            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            国民党的“联共”与“反共”的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 22 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1444340">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1444340/" class="title-link">隐微著述</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1444340"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1796479/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1796479-36.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1796479/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Thomas</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-07-19"
      class="main-meta">2008-07-19 17:29:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1444340_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    关于国共关系的历史考察，中共早期的活动，在国内既是重点热点同时又是禁区，于是那些党校学院的一大批党棍学阀们就一直以媲美苏联联共党史的真实度炮制一本又一本重复谎言与废话的垃圾，以至于对广大文艺青年来说，中国革命史完全成了一个不值得关注的阅读领域。   其实这段...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1444340/#comments">(29回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">30有用 / 8没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1444340_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1444340_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2199341">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2199341/" class="title-link">一切主义之争，终究是利益之争</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2199341"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/reasonlu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1056216-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/reasonlu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">那边</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-06"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-06 01:19:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2199341_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        还是验证了英国人的那句话：没有永远的朋友，也没有永远的敌人，只有永远的利益。杨奎松这本书，则又告诉我们一切主义之争，也不过是利益之争。     比如，按书中所述，对于战后和平谈判。并非如之前浩瀚书卷所说，国民党利用谈判，共产党真诚谈判。其实两党的态度大同小...

